'''Santini SMS''' 是一個義大利[[自行車|自行車]]服品牌，全名為「Santini Maglificio Sportivo」。由[[Pietro_Santini|Pietro Santini]]在1965年於[[義大利|義大利]][[拉廖_(科莫省)|拉廖]]成立。<ref name="UCI">[http://www.uci.ch/Modules/ENews/ENewsDetails.asp?id=OTYyNA&MenuId=MTI2Mjc "UCI renews partnership contract with Santini" Press release UCI, 13 September 2013]</ref> 創辦人少年喜歡騎車，後來接手姊姊們的紡織廠<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.santinisms.it/en/content/about-us-11|title=MADE IN ITALY, MADE WITH PASSION|accessdate=2017-03-13|author=|date=|publisher=|archive-date=2017-03-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170313214535/https://www.santinisms.it/en/content/about-us-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>，轉型成為製作及設計自行車服飾，並堅持產品線留在義大利本土生產。{{infobox brand|name=Santini SMS|logo=|image=|caption=Made in Italy, made with passion|type=自行車服飾|currentowner=Santini Maglificio Sportivo|origin=義大利|introduced=1965|discontinued=|related=|markets=全球|previousowners=|trademarkregistrations=Lallio (BG) ITALY|ambassadors=|tagline=Made in Italy, made with passion.|website=[http://www.santinisms.it/ santinisms.it]
